        <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: var(--text-3xl); font-family: var(--font-display); color: var(--text-primary); text-align: center;">ANN M. THANE</p>
        <p class="meta" style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: var(--text-sm); letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-sage); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">artist • explorer • mom</p>
      </div>
      <div class="press-list">
        
        <!-- Press Item 1 -->
        <article class="press-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="press-meta">
            <span class="press-date">November 2023</span>
            <span class="press-source">Bold Journeys</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="press-title">Interview with Bold Journeys</h3>
          <p class="press-excerpt">Thank you to online journal BOLD JOURNEYS for their recent conversation. I’m truly humbled to be included in such company.</p>
          <a href="https://boldjourney.com/meet-ann-m-thane/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Read Article</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Press Item 2 -->
        <article class="press-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="press-meta">
            <span class="press-date">January 2023</span>
            <span class="press-source">518 Profiles Magazine</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="press-title">Feature Overview</h3>
          <p class="press-excerpt">Thank you to Publisher Stephanie Stittnick and Author Carol St.Sauveur Ferris for the lovely overview, featuring many photos of my work on page 36.</p>
          <a href="https://issuu.com/ininkny/docs/2023_february_518_profiles_magazine" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">View Magazine</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Press Item 3 -->
        <article class="press-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="press-meta">
            <span class="press-date">March 1, 2020</span>
            <span class="press-source">The Daily Gazette</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="press-title">Former Mayor Just Wants to Make Art</h3>
          <p class="press-excerpt">A piece by Sara Foss covering the exhibition at the Perella Art Gallery, Fulton Montgomery Community College (Feb 2020 – Mar 2021).</p>
          <a href="https://dailygazette.com/article/2020/03/01/foss-former-mayor-just-wants-to-make-art" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline" style="padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.85rem;">Read Article</a>
        </article>

        <!-- Grant Item -->
        <article class="press-card grant-card" data-reveal>
          <div class="press-meta">
            <span class="press-source" style="color: var(--accent-gold);">Community Arts Grant</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="press-title">The Mother Mosaic Project</h3>
          <p class="press-excerpt">We were awarded $2,500 for the Mother Mosaic project, helping secure materials, studio space, and kiln usage. This program was made possible by Saratoga Arts with a Community Arts Grant funded by the New York State Council on the Arts.</p>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>


